{"tid":674060,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"今年秦國11月可能又政變,大家小心","createTime":"2018-05-22T11:20:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-25T20:14:03.000Z","uid":65346,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0408f805af7b7ecb0f3d96e7e2c2920921331d11","tid":674060,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T11:20:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"051b704d3da917a431039dd0eb77fd7d55314dfa","tid":674060,"uid":135645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T11:22:02.000Z","msg":"Source?"},{"pid":"294440dcb0dbafb1d14de8f1fd12f327161b8a69","tid":674060,"uid":161924,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T11:23:02.000Z","msg":"邊個推翻嬴政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cfbde80f1fc5a4ab18b24c8a088471e78b498dc","tid":674060,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T11:27:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1222077/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1222077%2F&d=4%2Fonko0djVBA3rAAniKUfr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=407834ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1222077%2F&h=035b5688\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1222077/</a><br />\n<br />\n周二（22日）是泰國軍政府執政滿四周年的日子，也是軍方發動政變四周年。數百名示威者周一晚在曼谷的法政大學紮營過夜，準備周二一早就遊行到政府大樓，表達對軍人奪權的不滿。但警方警告集會違反禁令，設置路障，並展開保安檢查，阻撓示威者遊行前往政府大樓。<br />\n<br />\n集會活動自周一晚開始，以演講和演唱方式進行。周二上午7時許，有逾500人開始集結，軍警不敢大意，派出優勢警力及大批部隊維持秩序，並阻擋群眾前往總理府，至上午9時半，仍在法政大學外道路僵持中。<br />\n<br />\n現場並未有衝突場面，活動中群眾手持標語和看板表達對軍政府的不滿，也反對國家和平秩序委員會的設立。雙方又透過麥克風相互喊話叫陣。反軍政府人士和民眾在法政大學外道路集會時，提出3點訴求，分別是如期在11月舉行大選、國家和平秩序委員會退場，以及軍隊不要支持國家和平秩序委員會。<br />\n<br />\n國家和平秩序委員會是由泰國軍警組成的委員會，主要目標是恢復並維持泰國社會秩序和實施政治改革。反對派人士指出，軍政府在2014年5月22日發動政變上台至今4年，人民生活並未過得比較好，貪污腐敗的情況依舊，同時限制政黨活動及箝制反政府人士的言論自由，舉行大選的時間也一直在變。 <br />\n<br />\n在周一，泰國警方已宣布政府大樓及其周邊街區將列為遊行禁區，並提醒示威者不要違反禁止超過五人集會的禁令。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">巴育原本承諾於今年11月舉行大選，不過之後卻不斷押後大選日子，目前已推遲至明年2月，但有民眾擔心政府會一拖再拖，恐怕大選會無了期押後。</span>"},{"pid":"104abbbd2ab2bac9092784dfa8af26844d3d2f61","tid":674060,"uid":29928,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T11:34:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">誰無誰</span></span>"},{"pid":"26a884a7583c91bc15d290212c3ec367cd3917a1","tid":674060,"uid":76855,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T11:59:17.000Z","msg":"<em></em>買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"094854a90540ae401dc32cdb0c7e241d84186d2f","tid":674060,"uid":163758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"294440dcb0dbafb1d14de8f1fd12f327161b8a69","tid":674060,"uid":161924,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T11:23:02.000Z","msg":"邊個推翻嬴政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T12:00:21.000Z","msg":"天子神劍"},{"pid":"2103ad5c79f7a3b92c851f79d60a3fac84246ad0","tid":674060,"uid":163758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"094854a90540ae401dc32cdb0c7e241d84186d2f","tid":674060,"uid":163758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"294440dcb0dbafb1d14de8f1fd12f327161b8a69","tid":674060,"uid":161924,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T11:23:02.000Z","msg":"邊個推翻嬴政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T12:00:21.000Z","msg":"天子神劍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T12:01:46.000Z",